(2,	3,	2,	1,	'2011-12-09',	'<p><strong>Geospatial Publication Investment</strong></p>\r\n<p>Compiled information for the SLM Business Case document on 12/5/11.&nbsp; Prepared Risk Management Log and Change Mangement Log on 12/5/11.</p>\r\n<p>Worked with Fred on 12/6/11 to provide support to GPI in regards to the overall project planning.&nbsp; We discussed GPI\'s work breakdown flow and how we could&nbsp;help the team could better understand supporting technologies.</p>\r\n<p>Discussed GPI\'s status via phone with Beth on 12/6/11.&nbsp; She had several questions about the ITIB presentation in January.&nbsp; I requested clarification from Al\'Tariq via email.</p>\r\n<p>Al\'Tariq provided clarification on 12/7/11.&nbsp; He agree that the presentation would include the following items: Scope, High Level Requirements, Benefits, Outline of Alternatives, Cost for Planning, Items included in Planning.</p>\r\n<p>Worked with Fred&nbsp;to compile appropriate questions for the GPI team to&nbsp;evaluate in regards to integrating with the systems where they will be obtaining data from on 12/7/11. Provided&nbsp;Beth with&nbsp;integration quesitons and explanations on 12/8/11.&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong>SLM</strong></p>\r\n<p>\r\n<p>Discussed Project Charter template along with the status of the Geospatial Publication and AFMSS in regards to the SLM process with Mr. Lewis and Fred on 12/7/11.&nbsp; We are reviewing templates to ensure that they are tailored specifically to BLM\'s needs.</p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p><strong>New Media/Social Media</strong></p>\r\n<p>Met with Al\'Tariq on 12/8/11 to discuss current version of strategy and information needed for the meeting on 12/8/11.&nbsp; Prepared a table listing team comments and revisions for review during the meeting.</p>\r\n<p>Reviewed strategy for alignment on 12/9/11.&nbsp; Reviewed additional comments from team leads regarding objective of the Strategy.&nbsp; Alexandra is preparing a Problem Statement.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Other</stron