/17/12 to discuss Acquisition Strategy documentation  after noticing several existing versions in other areas of BLM.&nbsp; <strong></strong></p>\r\n<p>Met with Fred on 1/19/12 to discuss sharepoint sites where SLM documents and PMO documents were posted.&nbsp;</p>',	'<p><strong>New Media</strong></p>\r\n<p>Met  with Al\'Tariq on 1/17/12 to discuss WO 600\'s/Kaveh\'s email.&nbsp; He thought  the revised bullets were a good idea and has a meeting scheduled with  Kaveh on 1/17/12.</p>\r\n<p>Met with Al\'Tariq on 1/18/12 to  discuss New Media Strategy status and meeting with Ronnie.&nbsp; We discussed  the Next Steps and Concerns from WO 600.&nbsp; Updated presentation to  include Ronnies Next Steps and the Interdiciplinary Teams Next Steps  along with a slide noting major concerns for meeting with Ronnie on  1/18/12.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Met with Ronnie and Al\'Tariq on 1/18/12 to discuss  presentation and meeting with the Exective Team.&nbsp; Ronnie approved the  presentaiton and requested that the Next Steps slide be combined.&nbsp; She  also requested that we meet with the executives individually prior to a  meeting with the entire team.&nbsp; This includes a meetin with NPS and Neil  Kornze.</p>\r\n<p><strong>SLM</strong></p>\r\n<p>Met with Fred on 1/17/12 to discuss Acquisition Strategy documentation  after noticing several existing versions in other areas of BLM.&nbsp; Fred is  reviewing the documents.<strong></strong></p>\r\n<p>Met with Fred on 1/19/12 to discuss sharepoint sites where SLM documents and PMO documents were posted.&nbsp; The SLM documents posted are not part of the current SLM.&nbsp;  Fred stated that he would discuss this with Al\'Tariq.&nbsp; The PMO documents  reflect a similar process to SLM.&nbsp; We discussed the confusion of having  two processes that are duplicating efforts.&nbsp; Fred stated that he would  look into this further.</p>',	'<p>na</p>',	'<p>na</p>',	2,	4,	'2012-01-20 18:09:57',	3,	'2012-01-25 03:33:38'),
(17,	6,	1,	1,	'2012-01-20',	'<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<ul style=\"padding-top: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; background-color: #fafafa; margin: 0px;\">\r\n<li style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px;\">Looked for some records management templates that we can add to the SLM repository. &nbsp;Have not found any at this point.</li>\r\n<li style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px;\">Had discussion with Naomi regarding the GeoComm project.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<ul style=\"padding-top: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; background-color: #fafafa; margin: 0px;\">\r\n<li style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px;\">Working on making a &nbsp;suggestion list for the GeoComm project. &nbsp;Will get this list to Naomi sometime early next week.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<ul style=\"padding-top: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; background-color: #fafafa; margin: 0px;\">\r\n<li style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px;\">Checked on the status of the SLM IM. &nbsp;Currently there is no new updated status for the SLM IM. &nbsp;</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<ul style=\"padding-top: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; background-color: #fafafa; margin: 0px;\">\r\n<li style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px;\">Had some discussions with Naomi regarding the New Media Project. &nbsp;Will provide Naomi a suggestion list early next week.</li>\r\n<li style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px;\">Working with Mohammad to restrict access to the existing SLM sharepoint sites. &nbsp;This will greatly help us in preparing to setup the new SLM sharepoint space.</li>\r\n<li style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px;\">Contacted Gail from the NOC to request comments on the SLM handbook.</li>\r\n<li style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 