ow well the teams had worked together.<span>&nbsp; </span>She suggested that we add a break line on the presentation to show that we were only discussing Planning and Requirements at this point.<span>&nbsp; </span>She understood that Execution included Design - O&amp;M and that potion would be broken out after the GPI team returned after the Planning Phase.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span>&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span>Met with Carmel Walters on 2/22/12 to discuss the project charter as they were packaging it for signature.<span>&nbsp; </span>We discussed BLM\'s format and WO570\'s format.<span>&nbsp; </span>She wanted to ensure that is was in the format that we wanted.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span>&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span>Worked with Beth and team 2/21/12 -2/24/12 in order to update ITIB documents and the presentation.<span>&nbsp; </span>Coordinated several impromtu meetings to ensure that WO300 and WO500 were on the same page.<span>&nbsp; </span>Provided updates to the charter and the presentation.<span>&nbsp; </span>Provided research for costs along with research information for RFI\'s and Contracts.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span>&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong><span>Field Focused Team</span></strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span>&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span>Met with the Field Focused team to discuss document tracking system efforts on 2/22/12.<span>&nbsp; </span>Mohammad suggested that we use a system developed by Lewis Technologies(Atechra).<span>&nbsp; </span>This was a sharepoint system previously viewed by some staff members.<span>&nbsp; </span>There is a requirements document that is provided with this.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span>&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong><span>Quicktime Information Bulletin</span></strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><!--[if gte mso 9]><xml> <o:OfficeDocumentSettings> 