(115,	13,	2,	1,	'2012-10-26',	'<p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">Began preparations for visit to GLO next week with NOC, GLO and WO500 Personnel regarding their workflows, systems and the upcoming move, coupled with Data Center Closure.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">Received new assignment to produce all project documentation for PPM Tool Project Began working on first docs, MND, Charter, ConOps</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n</p>',	'<p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">Provided assistance to CTO in finalizing ITIB presentation</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">Delivered a first draft MNS for PPM Tool Project</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n</p>',	'<p class=\"MsoNormal\">Attended PPM tool demonstration by consulting company representing HP.&nbsp; Staff consensus seemed to be that we all hope the tool works well, but didn&rsquo;t see much evidence of it in the&nbsp;presentation.</p>\r\n<p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">Weekly FDCCI telecon featured OPM personnel discussing the TCO model. &nbsp;Difficult to see how it can be useful on any but very large scale activities. &nbsp;Too many rounding error possibilities.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">Learned that all WO500 personnel are to be &ldquo;Google Guides&rdquo;, early adopter/tester/mentors, and that training was necessary; took first short training course.</p>\r\n</p>',	'<p>None.</p>',	'<p>N/A</p>',	2,	4,	'2012-10-30 12:43:52',	4,	'2012-10-31 17:36:10'),
(116,	2,	8,	1,	'2012-10-26',	'<p>AFMSS II - Worked on AFMSS II comments and changes to the Project Charter. Worked on&nbsp;comments and changes to RFP for&nbsp;the full AFMSS II Project.&nbsp; Worked on cost projections for FTEs associated with the planning phase of the project.</p>\r\n<p>AFMSS II APD - No activity<br /><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><span style=\"font-family: Symbol; mso-fareast-font-family: Symbol; mso-bidi-font-family: Symbol;\"><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore;\"><span style=\"font: 7pt \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span></span></span><br />TABLET PC -&nbsp;Turned over project to Chief Technology Officer.</p>\r\n<p>REA - Developed REA Lessons learned documentation for WO-200, WO-300,&nbsp;and NOC.</p>\r\n<p>NLSS -&nbsp;No activity.</p>\r\n<p>MDT - Worked on RFP issuance</p>',	'<p>AFMSS II - Completed acquisition plan for AFMSS II APD module.</p>\r\n<p>REA - completed lessons learned documentation.</p>\r\n<p>TABLET PC - Reviewed CA State Office justification for transition from blackberry to iPhone/Andriod devices.&nbsp; Turned over to Chief Technology Officer for complete BLM analysis.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>',	'<p>MDT - Bi-Weekly planning meeting.</p>\r\n<p>Portfolio Management Team - Demo/Presentation</p>\r\n<p>WO-570 -Bi-weekly</p>',	'<p>MDT - Still need assistance to get the RFP submitted.&nbsp; FWS has failed to the RFP to the BPA Contractor for a month.</p>',	'<p>None at this time.</p>',	2,	1,	'2012-11-01 09:57:41',	2,	'2012-11-01 10:13:28'),
(117,	16,	2,	1,	'2012-11-02',	'<p>\r\n<p style=\"line-height: 12.6pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">I met with Mohammad Haniffa to discuss project portfolio&rsquo;s future plan.&nbsp; Currently, he liked what I had done so far.&nbsp; He wants me to focus on comparing different projects and what technology they are using (i.e. databases, server OS, middleware and using GIS or not).&nbsp; This would be part of my weekly report to him.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"line-height: 115%; font-size: 10.5pt;\">Based on meeting with Mohammad, I started to collect data for the project portfolio comparison.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; I am looking at the databases, middleware, Server OS, Web Server, Reporting tools and other tools being used for the projects.&nbsp; </span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"line-height: 115%; font-size: 10.5pt;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"line-height: 115%; font-size: 10.5pt;\">As part of the bureau&rsquo;s move to Bison Connect, Department-wide email and calendar system, I took online course of Google Mail and Calendar.&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n</p>',	'<p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"line-height: 115%; font-size: 10.5pt;\">Project Portfolio &ndash; Started collecting data for different project I have been assigned to.&nbsp; This data would be useful in comparing similarities/differences between project portfolios.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"line-height: 115%; font-size: 10.5pt;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"line-height: 115%; font-size: 10.5pt;\">Bison Connect Project - As part of DOI&rsquo;s migration to Google e-mail and calendar project (Bison connect), I have finished Google e-mail and Calendar training required before going to Google Mail solution.</span></p>\r\n</p>',	'<p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"line-height: 115%; font-size: 10.5pt;\">Met one -on -one with Mohammad to discuss future plan for the project portfolio work.&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n</p>',	'<p>n/a</p>',	'<p>n/a</p>',	2,	4,	'2012-11-02 15:44:50',	4,	'2012-11-04 22:39:29'),
(118,	13,	2,	1,	'2012-11-02',	'<p>Hurricane shortened the week by two days.</p>\r\n<p>Joined CTO Stingley and NOC engineer at the General Land Office for a tour to gain initial understanding of their processes.&nbsp; Intent is to do Business Process Modeling to arrive at a workable architecture before moving them.&nbsp; They will be moving somewhere in DC metro area when realty finds them a suitable building (with a vault). They are digitizing all of the land records, but are not complete, need to gain detailed understanding of whether they can work in DC and locate servers in either the cloud or at NOC.&nbsp; Recent addition of a second firewall has slowed afternoon traffic to a standstill.</p>\r\n<p>Continued drafting the Charter for the PPM Tool Implementation.</p>\r\n<p>Assisted Mr. Samuels and Mr. Stingley in finalizing the FDCCI presentation for ITIB next week.</p>',	'<p>Completed an initial draft of the PPM Tool Charter&nbsp;and delivered to Ms. Bowers. Contains strategic goals addressed by solution, detailed requirements from RFP, etc.</p>',	'<p>Above-mentioned GLO tour and work on ITIB presentation.</p>',	'<p>None</p>',	'<p>N/A</p>',	2,	4,	'2012-11-02 16:43:52',	4,	'2012-11-04 22:43:30'),
