 next steps needed for the SPATS project.</span><span style=\"font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 115%;\">&nbsp; </span><span style=\"font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 115%;\">Mohammad will be giving me the project status template once Naomi is done modifying the template.</span><span style=\"font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 115%;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"line-height: 115%; font-size: 10.5pt;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"line-height: 115%; font-size: 10.5pt;\">Attended a meeting called by Taqueer (part of IT Investment Management team) to discuss Investment Profile Demo and High level update on IT Spend Plans</span>.&nbsp; Taqueer showed IT investment profile as an example and what we need to fill out once given to us.&nbsp; As a project portfolio team, I will be responsible for filling out information required by OMB by monthly and quarterly basis.&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>\r\n</p>',	'<p>n/a</p>',	'<p>n/a</p>',	2,	4,	'2012-12-28 15:07:55',	4,	'2013-01-04 22:56:50'),
