(179,	13,	17,	5,	'2013-03-01',	'<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong>Portfolio Management:&nbsp; </strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong>GPM: &nbsp;</strong>Business Manager is re-forming Integrated Program Team into separate business and technical teams.&nbsp; I will be on the technical team, Ms. Bowers on the business team.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">Reviewed GeoPortal Site after having plugin installed, as a possible vehicle for GPM; already carries USGS Landsat data. Site is not yet fully operational but appears promising.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong>PPM Tool Documentation:&nbsp; </strong>Began work on security documentation for new tool to meet requirements of the Operations Review Board. PIA document nearly complete (missing Records input). BLM Privacy Act Officer believes the tool will not require a SORN.&nbsp; Also began writing the Risk Management Plan, perhaps 30% complete.&nbsp; Will start on the Security Impact Assessment next week.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">Steady-State: &nbsp;</span></strong><span style=\"color: #595959; font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 115%;\">The following applications/systems are steady-state.&nbsp; Portfolio management oversight activities are being performed, including verification that systems are operating as expected and meeting the required standards for availability, reliability and security.&nbsp; System owners and stakeholders are periodically queried to identify new requirements, technical advances and overall system needs.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"Default\" style=\"line-height: 115%;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 115%; color: #595959; mso-themecolor: text1; mso-themetint: 166;\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"color: #595959; font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 115%;\">&nbsp; &