 class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong><span style=\"color: #222222; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;\">RAS</span></strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong><span style=\"color: #222222; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;\">NISIMS</span></strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"color: #222222; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;\"><br /></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n</p>',	'<p>\r\n<p><strong>FORVIS and RIPARIAN</strong></p>\r\n<p>(1)<span style=\"white-space: pre;\"> </span>Presented finding from Investment Profile (IP) to Portfolio Manager.</p>\r\n<p>(2)<span style=\"white-space: pre;\"> </span>Discussed the root cause of the IP discrepancy with Portfolio Manager.</p>\r\n<p><strong>SPATS</strong></p>\r\n<p>(1)<span style=\"white-space: pre;\"> </span>Completed the Risk management, Security and Privacy and Enterprise Architecture (EA) of the Business Case document</p>\r\n<p>(2)<span style=\"white-space: pre;\"> </span>Finished the Project Risk, Project Constraints, and Major Milestone section of the Project Charter document</p>\r\n<p><strong>Project Portfolio Management Tool Implementation</strong></p>\r\n<p>(1)<span style=\"white-space: pre;\"> </span>Articulated the current business process and gaps to the third party vendor for the Portfolio Management Tool implementation.</p>\r\n</p>',	'<p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong><span>WO-200 Project Status</span></strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; line-height: normal; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\"><strong><span>&nbsp;</span></strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span>Met with the Portfolio Manager to give status of my projects for our weekly meeting.&nbsp; Presented finding of Investment Profiles (IP) and gave status of the SPATS Business Case, Charter and Project Management Plan (PMP).</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span>&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height: 12.6pt; background-p